extendedInfo.description: Discover a truly remarkable vacation destination: Branson, Missouri. Whether you are looking to stay in a quiet lakefront cottage or in a beautiful hotel located right in the middle of the 76 Strip within walking distance of many shows and attractions, Use the new Choose Branson mobile application to assist you while in Branson.Need help with the colored routes? Yup we got it!Like tickets deals to the hottest shows? Purchase from your mobile device!Our app also allows for Facebook interaction, see what people like! There are also videos and a Live Album where you can share your experience right from your mobile device with others. So why wait! Install this exciting app today!
